AETHERMUD STAFF COMMAND: SETROLE

SYNTAX
  setrole <player> <admin|domain|coding|rp>

DESCRIPTION
  Sets a wizard's position and synced role tag. The target must be
  online and must already be a wizard (including Apprentice).

    admin   -> arch         [Admin-Wiz]
    domain  -> domain_wiz   [Domain-Wiz]
    coding  -> creator      [Coding-Wiz]
    rp      -> rp_wiz       [RP-Wiz]

  Restricted to admin-level wizards. Position and role are saved
  immediately.

PROMOTING A MORTAL FIRST
  If the player is still a mortal, use makewiz first. That creates an
  Apprentice. After apprenticeship tasks, assign the full role:

    makewiz splynncryth
    setrole splynncryth admin

  Or use the Staff of Demotion (type: promote) for a menu-driven
  approach to full roles (not Apprentice).

NOTES
  - setrole only works on online players.
  - Use xmote for offline position changes (admin only).
  - All role changes are logged to /log/adm/setrole.

